{"id": "art-940", "label": "Art. 940", "title": "Art. 940: Judecata", "slug": "art-940", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_430616567\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1083\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_430616567\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 940:\nJudecata </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2136810767\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1082\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2136810767\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dup&#259; primirea actelor prev&#259;zute la art. 938 se\nva fixa termenul pentru judecarea cererii, dispunându-se citarea\np&#259;r&#355;ilor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_713615905\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1081\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_713615905\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Judecarea cererii se face de urgen&#355;&#259; &#351;i\ncu prec&#259;dere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_980130558\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1080\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_980130558\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)La termenul de judecat&#259;, instan&#355;a este\nobligat&#259; s&#259; îl asculte, în camera de consiliu, pe cel a c&#259;rui\npunere sub ocrotire este cerut&#259;, punându-i &#351;i întreb&#259;ri pentru a\nconstata necesitatea &#351;i oportunitatea instituirii unei m&#259;suri de\nocrotire, precum &#351;i opinia sa cu privire la regimul de ocrotire &#351;i la\npersoana ocrotitorului. Dac&#259; este în interesul celui a c&#259;rui punere\nsub ocrotire este cerut&#259;, acesta va fi ascultat la locuin&#355;a sa, acolo\nunde este îngrijit sau în alt loc apreciat de instan&#355;&#259; ca fiind\npotrivit.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_360725988\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1079\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_360725988\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)La ascultarea celui a c&#259;rui ocrotire se\nsolicit&#259; poate fi de fa&#355;&#259; o persoan&#259; de încredere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_72150240\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1078\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_72150240\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Prin excep&#355;ie, prelungirea m&#259;surii tutelei\nspeciale pentru o durat&#259; mai mare de 5 ani se poate dispune f&#259;r&#259;\nascultarea persoanei ocrotite dac&#259; în raportul medical se\nmen&#355;ioneaz&#259; c&#259; ascultarea sa este de natur&#259; s&#259;\naduc&#259; atingere st&#259;rii ei de s&#259;n&#259;tate sau aceasta nu este în\nm&#259;sur&#259; s&#259; î&#351;i exprime voin&#355;a.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1207058438\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1077\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1207058438\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Judecarea se face cu participarea procurorului. Atunci\ncând reclamantul renun&#355;&#259; la judecat&#259;, procurorul poate cere\ncontinuarea judec&#259;&#355;ii. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 81 alin. (2) se\naplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_239904460\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1076\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_239904460\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Pe întreaga durat&#259; a procedurii, persoana a\nc&#259;rei ocrotire se cere va fi informat&#259;, în modalit&#259;&#355;i\nadaptate st&#259;rii acesteia, despre desf&#259;&#351;urarea procedurii\njudiciare, precum &#351;i despre luarea oric&#259;rei m&#259;suri cu privire la\npersoana &#351;i bunurile sale.</span></p>"}